# Vendored runtime helpers (adb + scrcpy-server). These ship next to
# 1PhoneMirror.exe and are copied into the build output by CMake. The
# global *.exe / *.dll ignores above would otherwise drop them.
!tools/
!tools/**
!tools/**/*.exe
!tools/**/*.dll

